org.spongepowered.api.service.economy.account

Interface UniqueAccount

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Account, Contextual, Identifiable

    public interface UniqueAccount
extends Account, Identifiable
    Represents an Account identified by a UUID.

    This is usually linked to a particular User's GameProfile, through Identifiable.getUniqueId().
